SESSION 2026-05-28 (cont.) — get_token.py: daily OAuth token automation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

[2026-05-28] get_token.py :: Created. Automates the daily Upstox token refresh:
  reads api_key/api_secret/redirect_url from .env, opens browser to OAuth login,
  prompts user to paste the redirect URL (contains ?code=), extracts the code,
  POSTs to Upstox token exchange endpoint, writes UPSTOX_ACCESS_TOKEN back to
  .env via dotenv.set_key(). Prints "Token saved. Valid until midnight."

[2026-05-28] live_trader.py :: Docstring updated to say "run get_token.py each
  morning" instead of manually editing .env. Added module-level
  ACCESS_TOKEN = os.getenv('UPSTOX_ACCESS_TOKEN') after load_dotenv().
  _get_token() now references ACCESS_TOKEN and error message points to
  get_token.py instead of the Upstox developer console.

